simple-logger provides a lightweight logging library.

Usage:
    find_package(simple-logger CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE simple-logger::simple-logger)

Example:
    #include <simple-logger/logger.hpp>
    simple::logger::instance().add_console_sink();
    simple::logger::instance().add_file_sink("app.log");
    LOG_INFO("Main", "Application started");
    LOG_ERROR("Network", "Connection failed");
